Package: microecoshiny
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Microbiome Data Analysis Based on microeco
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chi Liu", "Developer", email = "liuchi0426@126.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4055-8677"))
  )
Description: An interactive Shiny application for comprehensive microbiome data analysis.
    Built on top of the microeco R package, providing a user-friendly web interface
    for data import, preprocessing, normalization, diversity analysis, differential
    abundance testing, network analysis, null model analysis, functional prediction,
    and machine learning classification. Supports QIIME2, BIOM, and standard file formats.
